UI_setting_battleTimer_tooltip:
Enables voice notification about remaining time in battle:
 • 15 minutes remaining (battle start);
 • 5 minutes remaining;
 • 3 minutes remaining;
 • 2 minutes remaining;
 • 1 minute remaining;
 • 30 seconds remaining;
 • 10 seconds remaining;
 • 5 seconds countdown;
 • Battle is over.
